INSERT INTO `landscaping_works_collections` VALUES (1,'z14z4j8e00115i6nhwr67fw0','Civil Engineering and Development Department Contract No. CV/2013/08 Liantang / Heung Yuen Wai Boundary Control Point Site Formation and Infrastructure Works – Contract 6','Civil Engineering and Development Department Contract No. CV/2013/08 Liantang / Heung Yuen Wai Boundary Control Point Site Formation and Infrastructure Works – Contract 6','Civil Engineering and Development Department','24 June 2015 - 21 June 2019','<p>The LT/HYW BCP is the seventh land-based BCP between Hong Kong and Shenzhen. At present, there are two land-based BCPs at Man Kam To and Sha Tau Kok. Owing to geographical constraints, however, these two BCPs have little room for further expansion. Situated between Man Kam To and Sha Tau Kok, the LT/HYW BCP will make up for the inadequacies and make cross-boundary transportation and connections between Hong Kong and the eastern part of Guangdong Province as well as the Fujian and Jiangxi Provinces more convenient and efficient. This can help expand Hong Kong&#x27;s economic hinterland.</p><p>It comprises the construction of an approximately 4.6km long dual two-lane Connecting Road connecting the BCP with the proposed Sha Tau Kok Interchange and the associated tunnel ventilation buildings. Provision of sewage collection, treatment and disposal facilities for the BCP and the resite of Chuk Yuen Village and the associated environmental mitigation measures, and Environmental Monitoring and Audit (EM&amp;A)</p>','2025-06-03 02:20:27.678000','2025-07-07 07:18:38.903000',NULL,8,36,'en',1.00),(3,'zo9ves6l86lc3lhavonc939f','Contract No. HK/2012/08 – Wan Chai Development Phase II – Central – Wan Chai Bypass at Wan Chai West','Contract No. HK/2012/08 – Wan Chai Development Phase II – Central – Wan Chai Bypass at Wan Chai West','Civil Engineering and Development Department','31 January 2013 - 28 November 2018','<p>The key purpose of Wan Chai Development Phase II is to provide land at Wan Chai North and North Point for the construction of the Central - Wan Chai Bypass and Island Eastern Corridor Link. Land formed under the project will be developed as a world-class waterfront promenade for public enjoyment and solve the traffic problem around Wan Chai district.</p><p>This is one of the contract in Wan Chai Development Phase II. It is a large scale Reclamation Project with more than 5 Ha. in size. The Project&#x27;s location is from the Central Reclamation Phase III (CRIII) eastern seawall to the west of Hong Kong Convention and Exhibition Centre Extension. The scope of work includes dredging works, seawall works, watermains laying, demolition of existing Expo Drive West Bridge, box culvert extension and stormwater drainage works.</p>','2025-06-03 02:21:17.704000','2025-07-07 07:18:39.769000',NULL,8,36,'en',2.00),(5,'mg4uwpc42qy58z06w6m44usd','Uplifting Works to Promenades of Aberdeen Harbour and Ap Lei Chau Main Street Area (Contract No. CV/2011/02)','Uplifting Works to Promenades of Aberdeen Harbour and Ap Lei Chau Main Street Area','Civil Engineering and Development Department','30 September 2011 - 31 December 2014','<p>This is a Design and Build project for the uplifting works to promenades of Aberdeen Harbour and Ap Lei Chau Main Street Area. The objective of the works is to enhance the Aberdeen area and aim to further bring out the unique features of &#x27;traditional fishing harbour&#x27; and the local culture of Aberdeen and, by reinforcing the elements of diversified tourism, to enhance Aberdeen&#x27;s attractiveness to both international visitors and local residents.</p>','2025-06-03 02:22:33.929000','2025-07-07 07:18:38.409000',NULL,8,36,'en',3.00),(7,'qiifwf1y0ub2vm5cl140nr3v','Contract No. HY/2008/12 Bus-Bus Interchanges on Tuen Mun Road','Contract No. HY/2008/12 Bus-Bus Interchanges on Tuen Mun Road','Highways Department','15 July 2010 - 31 July 2015','<p>The works mainly comprise the construction of a bus-bus interchange on Tuen Mun Road Kowloon-bound near Siu Lam Interchange and Tai Lam Kok roundabout, the widening of Brothers&#x27; Bridge, and the construction of a link bridge with two lifts. It will allow passengers to travel on foot from the holding area at TMR to the holding area at Tai Lam Kok to switch buses. Two lifts will be constructed in connection with the link bridge to provide access to people with disabilities. Its associated civil works include road reconstruction, provision of shelters, drainage, landscaping, traffic aids and street lighting, slope works, waterworks, and provisioning of works for traffic control surveillance.</p><p>The project aims at providing a convenient interchange facility for passengers to switch amongst bus routes from/to Northwest New Territories operating via Tuen Mun Road. This arrangement will not only provide passengers more choices of bus services at the bus-bus interchange, but also greatly enhance the overall efficiency of the bus network in the Northwest New Territories and reduce traffic congestion and road-side air pollution.</p>','2025-06-03 02:23:14.842000','2025-07-07 07:18:37.822000',NULL,8,36,'en',4.00),(9,'inr3ibhxxdo6fyt98lhx40es','Greening Works in Kwun Tong (Contract No: CV/2009/06)','Greening Works in Kwun Tong','Civil Engineering and Development Department','25 September 2009 - 24 March 2011','<p>Hong Kong Government initiated a Greening Master Plan which provides an overall greening framework for various areas by identifying suitable locations for planting with appropriate themes and species to achieve a coherent design and a sustainable effect.</p><p>In year 2009, our group was awarded the greening works contract in Kwun Tong. The works comprise the planting and establishment of about 2,940 trees and 840,000 shrubs within Kwun Tong District and associated landscape hardworks including planters, irrigation facilities and associated pavement works.</p>','2025-06-03 02:24:00.691000','2025-07-07 07:18:39.144000',NULL,8,36,'en',5.00),(11,'qni7dkt9kn1r7470asinmvjc','Greening works in Urban Areas - Phase II (Contract No. CV/2008/02)','Greening works in Urban Areas - Phase II','ACLA Limited','29 August 2008 - 31 December 2009',NULL,'2025-06-03 02:25:57.458000','2025-07-07 07:18:38.755000',NULL,8,36,'en',6.00),(13,'hnbi1ru1ycy3cghoq1bub0cx','Retrofitting of Noise Barriers on Tsing Tsuen Bridge at Tsing Yi and Tsuen Wan Approaches (Contract No. HY/2007/08)','Retrofitting of Noise Barriers on Tsing Tsuen Bridge at Tsing Yi and Tsuen Wan Approaches','Highways Department','08 January 2008 - 09 July 2011','<p>The major elements of Works consisted of:</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Construction of noise barriers on Tsing Tsuen Bridgeat Tsing Yi and Tsuen Wan Approaches</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Associated structural modification works to existing bridge parapet and utility troughs</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Associated civil, geotechnical traffic aids, road pavement, drainage etc.</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Utilities diversion</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Landscaping works</li></ul>','2025-06-03 02:26:52.736000','2025-07-07 07:18:40.013000',NULL,8,36,'en',7.00),(15,'byqijjf8m60ilhd74ssgqawv','Road L18A in AREA 18, Tuen Mun (Contract No.TM/2006/02)','Road L18A in AREA 18, Tuen Mun','Civil Engineering and Development Department','30 April 2007 - 29 May 2009','<p>The major works in this project consisted of the construction of an approx. 400m long and 10.3m wide two-lane carriageway with a 3.5m wide footpath on both sides section of about 160m long elevated structure over Wong Chu Road was constructed with a total of about 135m of retaining wall structure at both ends of the elevated structure.</p>','2025-06-03 02:28:40.482000','2025-07-07 07:18:37.961000',NULL,8,36,'en',8.00),(17,'p77813f2fsd219m8j1yj4yz3','Development of EcoPark in Tuen Mun Area 38 (Contract No. EP/SP/52/06)','Development of EcoPark in Tuen Mun Area 38','Environmental Protection Department','03 July 2006 - 01 January 2010','<p>The EcoPark is a key element of the strategy that aims to promote the local recycling industry and jump-start a sustainable economy by providing long-term land facility for the environmental and recycling industry. By encouraging and promoting the reuse, recovery and recycling of our waste resources and return them to the consumption loop, the EcoPark will help capitalize the potential of the local recycling industry and alleviate the heavy demand of the Hong Kong landfills.</p><br/><p>EcoPark occupies 20 hectares of land in Tuen Mun Area 38 and will be developed in two phases. Phase I of EcoPark (about 8 ha) will be available for occupation towards the end of 2006 and Phase II (about 12 ha) in 2009. Various environmentally friendly features are being used for the first time in Hong Kong, such as the Sun Pipe, Solar power water faucet, and a Green roof just to name a few.</p>','2025-06-03 02:31:08.569000','2025-07-07 07:18:39.256000',NULL,8,36,'en',9.00),(19,'u1xe1dk6gyc0l3jejkyuyecw','Remaining Engineering Infrastructure Works for Pak Shek Kok Development, Package 2A (Contract No. TP37/03)','Remaining Engineering Infrastructure Works for Pak Shek Kok Development, Package 2A','Civil and Engineering Development Department','29 June 2004 - 15 October 2008','<p>This is the engineering infrastructure project for Pak Shek Kok Development.  The major works of the project consisted of a significant quantity of site formation works; and the construction of roads &amp; bridges, cycle track, water front promenade, subway, and the associated landscaping works, etc.</p>','2025-06-03 02:32:32.951000','2025-07-07 07:18:38.428000',NULL,8,36,'en',10.00),(21,'oaosn2r7rima9j3clq5s3b2a','土木工程拓展署合约编号CV/2013/08 - 莲塘/香园围口岸土地平整及基建工程 – 工程合约六','土木工程拓展署合约编号CV/2013/08 - 莲塘/香园围口岸土地平整及基建工程 – 工程合约六','土木工程拓展署','2015 年 06 月 24 日 - 2019 年 06 月 21 日','<p>莲塘/香园围口岸是香港、深圳之间第七个陆路口岸。现时文锦渡和沙头角两个陆路口岸，碍于地理限制，难有再扩建的空间。莲塘/香园围口岸位于文锦渡和沙头角之间，正好填补这个不足，使香港与广东省东部地区以至福建及江西的跨境交通连接更方便快捷。新口岸在策略上对推动长远经济发展十分重要。</p><p>兴建一条4.6公里的双程双线分隔主干道以连接沙头角公路交汇处及新口岸，提供排水/排污、水务及新口岸的公共设施工程，另外处理竹园村的迁移，相关的环境缓解措施，以及环境监测及稽核。</p>','2025-06-03 02:35:02.778000','2025-07-07 07:18:30.171000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN',1.00),(23,'u7k104hyle1ml7q5064hw5xa','HK / 2012/08湾仔发展计划第二期–中环湾仔绕道湾仔西段','HK / 2012/08湾仔发展计划第二期–中环湾仔绕道湾仔西段','土木工程拓展署','2013 年 01 月 31 日 - 2018 年 11 月 28 日','<p>湾仔发展计划第二期为湾仔北和北角提供土地，被兴建中环及湾仔绕道和东区走廊连接路。纾缓湾仔附近一带的交通问题</p><p>本合约是一项超过5公里的大型填海工程。其地盘位由中环填海计划第三期东面海堤延伸至香港会议展览中心新翼的西边。其合约范围内的工程包括：挖泥工程，海提建造;水管接头;清拆博览道西桥，箱型渠延长，以及建造雨水渠务工程</p>','2025-06-03 02:35:43.269000','2025-07-07 07:18:30.172000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN',2.00),(25,'pe5u6gqnriy2pozutvsko4yz','香港仔港湾兩岸海滨长廊和鸭脷洲大街 一带之美化工程 (合约编号CV/2011/02)','香港仔港湾兩岸海滨长廊和鸭脷洲大街 一带之美化工程','土木工程拓展署','2011 年 09 月 30 日 - 2014 年 12 月 31 日','<p>香港仔两岸海滨长廊和鸭脷洲大街一带之美化工程采用设计与建造合约形式。本工程主旨为改善香港仔两岸的旅游设施，进一步突显香港仔独有的&quot;传统渔港&quot;及本土文化特色，并加强多元化旅游的元素，以提升香港仔对海外旅客及本地居民的吸引力。</p>','2025-06-03 02:36:25.831000','2025-07-07 07:18:30.190000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN',3.00),(27,'p2gbj2yxa1udsv2jj9os8k2f','合约编号HY/2008/12屯门公路巴士转乘站','合约编号HY/2008/12屯门公路巴士转乘站','路政署','2010 年 07 月 15 日 - 2015 年 07 月 31 日','<p>该项工程主要包括在小榄交汇处附近的屯门公路往九龙方向及在大榄角回旋处附近的屯门公路往屯门方向辟设巴士转乘站，把兄弟桥扩阔，建造一条连接桥，可让乘客步行往来屯门公路及大榄角两个等候处转乘其他巴士线。连接桥上设有两部升降机，方便残障人士往来。另外进行附属工程，包括重建道路、建造上盖、渠务、环境美化、交通辅助设施、街道照明、斜坡、水务等工程及提供相关设施予交通管制监察系统。</p><p>这项工程旨在提供便利的巴士转乘设施，让乘客转乘取道屯门公路往来新界西北的各条巴士线。这项安排既能让现有乘客于转乘站有更多巴士路线的选择，又能大大提升新界西北巴士网络的整体效率，便利乘客，纾缓交通挤塞，以及减低路边空气污染。</p>','2025-06-03 02:37:52.326000','2025-07-07 07:18:30.173000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN',4.00),(29,'ica8tqsniel1g84ec0f9r2xc','观塘綠化工程 (合约编号 CV/2009/06)','观塘綠化工程','土木工程拓展署','2009 年 09 月 25 日 - 2011 年 03 月 24 日','<p>政府展开绿化总纲图计划的绿化工程，计划是透过研究地区的位置和特性，为地区订立适合的绿化大纲，并为规划、设计和推行有关工程提供指引。除了提供建议的种植地点外，绿化总纲图亦会确立绿化主题，及建议适合的栽种主题和植物品种，以取得持续和一致的绿化效果。</p><p>集团于2009年获得当中的观塘綠化工程合约。工程主要包括在观塘区内种植及培植约2,940棵树木及840,000棵灌木和相关景观设施，包括花槽，灌溉设施和相关的路面工程。</p>','2025-06-03 02:39:02.592000','2025-07-07 07:18:30.423000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN',5.00),(31,'lq6n060zm83yr2fm5t7isj05','市区余下地区的绿化工程 (合约编号：CV/2008/02)','市区余下地区的绿化工程','土木工程拓展署','2008 年 08 月 29 日 - 2009 年 12 月 31 日','<p>主要工程包括：</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>种植和培植约 4,200棵树及 1,000,000棵灌木</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>相关园景美化工程，包括灌溉设施及路面工程</li></ul><br/>','2025-06-03 02:39:53.545000','2025-07-07 07:18:30.601000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN',6.00),(33,'gh8mj1ziep8icm6w5q5u7vhn','位于青衣及荃湾引道的青荃桥的隔音屏障加建工程 (合约编号: HY/2007/08)','位于青衣及荃湾引道的青荃桥的隔音屏障加建工程','路政署','2008 年 01 月 08 日 - 2011 年 07 月 09 日','<p>工程主要包括:</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>位于青衣及荃湾引道的青荃桥的隔音屏障加建工程</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>对现有桥面护栏及并其它公共设施槽进行构造上的修改工程</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>进行相关的道路、渠务、土力、街道照明等工程</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>修改移动公用设施</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>环境美化工程</li></ul>','2025-06-03 02:41:04.514000','2025-07-07 07:18:30.375000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN',7.00),(35,'h6xmky3jzch6jk9laoovhqr0','屯门第18区L18A路道路工程 (合约编号：TM/2006/02)','屯门第18区L18A路道路工程','土木工程拓展署','2007 年 04 月 30 日 - 2009 年 05 月 29 日','<p>工程的主要项目包括建造一条长约 400米， 宽10.3米的双线行车道并两侧备有3.5米宽行人路; 及1段长约160米横跨皇珠路的高架桥并在桥两侧铺设长约 135米的挡土墙</p>','2025-06-03 02:41:49.221000','2025-07-07 07:18:30.364000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN',8.00),(37,'wfbtjx4exxpf5gn5m27p0yz0','屯门第38区环保园发展工程 (合约编号：EP/SP/52/06)','屯门第38区环保园发展工程','环境保护署','2006 年 07 月 03 日 - 2010 年 01 月 01 日','<p>环保园是一个关键因素的战略，其目的是促进本地循环再造业和快速激活一个可持续发展的经济提供长期的土地设施的环境及循环再造业。通过鼓励和促进再利用，回收和循环再造的废物资源，并返回他们的消费循环中，环保园将有助于利用的潜力本地循环再造业，减轻沉重的需求，香港的堆填区。</p><br/><p>环保园占地 20公顷的土地位于屯门第38区，将分两个阶段发展。环保园第一期（约 8公顷），将用于对结束占领和2006年第二期（约 12公顷）在2009年。各种环保设施正在使用首次在香港，如太阳管道，太阳能水龙头，并且有绿色屋顶等等</p>','2025-06-03 02:43:00.119000','2025-07-07 07:18:30.586000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN',9.00),(39,'pj28nqcqww0kaeyaprbj6bev','白石角发展计划基础设施工程 - 第 2A 阶段 (合约编号: TP