 / Heung Yuen Wai Boundary Control Point Site Formation and Infrastructure Works – Contract 6','Civil Engineering and Development Department Contract No. CV/2013/08 Liantang / Heung Yuen Wai Boundary Control Point Site Formation and Infrastructure Works – Contract 6','Civil Engineering and Development Department','24 June 2015 - 21 June 2019','<p>The LT/HYW BCP is the seventh land-based BCP between Hong Kong and Shenzhen. At present, there are two land-based BCPs at Man Kam To and Sha Tau Kok. Owing to geographical constraints, however, these two BCPs have little room for further expansion. Situated between Man Kam To and Sha Tau Kok, the LT/HYW BCP will make up for the inadequacies and make cross-boundary transportation and connections between Hong Kong and the eastern part of Guangdong Province as well as the Fujian and Jiangxi Provinces more convenient and efficient. This can help expand Hong Kong&#x27;s economic hinterland.</p><p>It comprises the construction of an approximately 4.6km long dual two-lane Connecting Road connecting the BCP with the proposed Sha Tau Kok Interchange and the associated tunnel ventilation buildings. Provision of sewage collection, treatment and disposal facilities for the BCP and the resite of Chuk Yuen Village and the associated environmental mitigation measures, and Environmental Monitoring and Audit (EM&amp;A)</p>','2025-06-03 02:20:27.678000','2025-07-07 07:18:38.903000','2025-07-07 07:18:39.148000',8,36,'en',1.00),(193,'flgov0wn6qfsbtlmuhc6jxqp','銅鑼灣行車天橋重建及相關的維園道擴闊工程 (合約編號：HY/2003/27)','銅鑼灣行車天橋重建及相關的維園道擴闊工程','路政署','2004 年 06 月 10 日 - 2008 年 05 月 29 日','<p>工 程 計 劃 包 括:</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>拆 卸 現 有 的 銅 鑼 灣 行 車 天 橋 和 毗 鄰 的 行 人 天 橋 ；</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建 造 一 條 連 接 東 行 之 維 園 道 與 南 行 之 告 士 打 道 的 210 米 長 的 雙 線 單 程 行 車 天 橋 ；</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建 造 一 條 橫 跨 維 園 道 的 有 蓋 行 人 天 橋 ；</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 l